Fantasia Crystals and Northern Winds have a great selection of everything. You can find a large selection of stones, statues, incense, totems, metaphysical books, essential oils, tools for rituals, etc. I go in every few weeks to buy incense and usually leave with a few new gemstones. They are constantly getting new inventory.  The staff is all super knowledgeable and ready and willing to help. I've interacted with everyone. They remember their regulars and they treat you like family.  In fact, I went in one day to ask for some metaphysical advice and Beth spent a good amount of time assessing the situation and walking me through various ways to help solve the problem. And it worked :)  This is a great shop!

