So these guys are pretty awesome!  My car was misfiring.  The first place I took it to said it was just my o2 sensor...it wasn't.  The second place was going to charge me upwards of $500 just for the diagnostics.  Ron quoted me a reasonable price to perform the diagnostic tests.  They also charged a reasonable price for labor and gave me a list of the other work I need to eventually have done.  These guys are honest and fast.  I'll be going back to them for sure.

